data.description: Nestled in the heart of Destin is this charming family home, that's been well maintained and lovingly taken care of. The kitchen offers granite counter tops and stainles steel appliances and it opens up to the dining/living room combo, great for entertaining and family gatherings. Large laundry room and a half bath are also downstairs along with ample storage underneath the staircase. You can enjoy your morning cofee or simply relax in the covered back patio, overlooking green area and the neigbourhood park. The second floor features newly installed hardwood flooring and the master bedroom with a good size walk in closet and double vanity in the master bath. Also on the secon level are two additional bedrooms and a full bath. For your piece of mind, the roof is only 2 years old and both the AC and hot water heater have been replaced within the last couple years. Two car garage and plenty of parking space on your large driveway. The neighbourhood offers a park with a playground and 2 lakefront green areas. Destin Elementary and  Highschool are just a short distance away, along with some great restaurants, grocery stores and of course the beautiful beaches. Call today to schedule your private showing.
